snippet.title: Black Myth: Wukong | Full Ray Tracing & NVIDIA DLSS 3.5 | PREMIERE
snippet.description:
Black Myth: Wukong is launching this August with full ray tracing and NVIDIA DLSS 3.5. 
https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/gdc-2024-dlss-rtx-full-ray-tracing-game-announcements/

Confront destiny in this action RPG rooted in Chinese mythology. Black Myth: Wukong is based on Journey to the West, one of the Four Great Classic Chinese Novels. 

Learn More about Black Myth: Wukong: https://www.heishenhua.com/

Subscribe to @NVIDIAGeForce today!
